Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡面放了剩的果醬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然如此無與倫比的難吃！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來真難吃！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說 美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問我沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能沒事啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俺可是因為這個如此難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果都看到微妙的走馬燈了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也想到了會很難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟然有這麼大的威力…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明明知道難吃為什麼還要做啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為感覺挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！這個白癡老姐！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 重來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是 什麼果醬～吶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰管啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正放了壞掉的魚吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:04:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正解是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹹圓鰺魚乾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}譯註：鹹圓鰺魚乾{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}（くさや）{\r\fs36} 與 壞掉的{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}（くさった）{\r\fs36} 音近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹹圓——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是第一次也是最後一次的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的鹹圓鰺魚乾紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:37.36,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,0)\frz270\bord4\blur8\pos(50,360)}ACCIDENT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小誠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天爸爸會晚回來 準備叫點外賣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想吃些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼弄得亂七八糟的啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了多少次他還是不收拾！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來不跟他生氣的話是不行的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:18.99,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\fnsimhei\pos(755,494)\frz2.785\c&H594CC0&}劇場版
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:18.99,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\fnsimhei\frz2.785\c&HBD83E0&\pos(763,543)}Helvitica\NStandard
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這這這這這這這這這這這難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難難難難難難難難難難難到說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你丫幹嗎呢啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是跟你說過不要隨便進來了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次你丫要是再進來的話我就要把你那什麼啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你丫！那什麼啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 今天一定要跟他發火…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說了！！不要隨便進來啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒… 呃 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 為啥要擅自收拾別人的屋子啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為小誠你一直都不收拾啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最完美了啊！！分佈！！就那樣！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之不要進我屋子啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小誠！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說！！為什麼要擅自進來啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說還太早了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說還太早了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說還太早了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你… 你你你你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你丫…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那那那那那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈——！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈——！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是我的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這可是從小誠的房間裡發現的哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈——？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒看到過那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 這裡雖然是我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是一開始就這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不一定就是我房間裡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之我覺得這種東西還太早了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈——？你在說什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢 我也完全不知道怎麼回事！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 我要把這個扔了哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那書！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是部長的東西！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要扔別人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是沒想到啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我剛才看了兩眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該說Amazing還是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不可以看這些東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得會變成不良少年啊你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦！！不看啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不看啦所以你不要擅自進我的屋子！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太糟啦真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼高崎老師會對這種——
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小誠… 你生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少給我敲敲門啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是… 我心想你可能生氣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒生氣哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 果然生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒生氣哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒生氣啊 所以你趕快出去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次你要是不敲門的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你丫就那什麼啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超級那什麼啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想一個人住…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚～～ 今天好失敗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他說了房間那樣子要打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那本書不是小誠的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是最近學校的同學們風紀很亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家&學校兩邊我都要好好幹啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我是學生指導！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 都忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小誠 準備訂外賣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得跟你說多少遍你才明白啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:24.73,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95\pos(150,150)}雪\N飄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:24.73,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fs24\pos(221,150)}flsnow
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\bord0\shad0\c&H262626&\pos(640,298)\frz2.095}畢業去向調查表
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\bord0\shad0\c&H262626&\frz2.095\pos(567,393)}班級                             姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs33\bord0\shad0\c&H262626&\frz2.095\pos(573,423)}現在 感興趣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\bord0\shad0\frz2.095\pos(583,534)\c&H99989A&}全球變暖 少子高齡化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs33\bord0\shad0\c&H262626&\frz2.095\pos(536,603)}將來的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 將來的希望這一欄裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼夢想或者目標什麼的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死之前想上一次電視
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是問的方式比較不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼想做的工作或者職業麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要做 像櫻井老師那樣的老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我 一樣的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是大家傳遞下來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紐帶！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你咯 中村！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的… 大學最後一次比賽 啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中途棄權
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時定大學在這裡棄權了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前去名乃家的途中遇到博士了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還被狗咬了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我們跟博士說聲「我們下次再去 拜託了」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.86,0:12:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請來做我們的顧問吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不做的事情就是不做啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前你不是都說OK了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？！我什麼時候說過那些話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇 真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是約好了跟老師決鬥 我贏了的話 就來當我們的顧問的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 那個時候不是平局的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒——
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的～ 我要跟大家洩漏你跟姐姐的事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活動室在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始圍棋足球部可以運作了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真 真是抱歉！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然開門了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帶來了新的顧問老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 我說！！等等！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑什麼跑！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高崎老師！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像跑掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來還想勸誘一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井不在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都弄不出來這個部的正經的說明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說來說去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正是我的部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 小鹿亂撞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼小菲要小鹿亂撞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為接下來要去告白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向那個叫中之條的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢！ 在這所和平的學校裡的那份朋克的精神！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫西乾果然就是有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…嘛 說有魅力倒不如說很有個性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師 請等一等！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說…  高崎老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要逃跑呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼熱情十足的圍棋足球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很久沒有那樣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了老師你 沒有顧問的人選了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也… 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和什麼相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用什麼 把什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 該怎麼說呢 用什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什… 都來到活動室了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…沒有辦法了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了這個 你還能說出那些話嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說… 你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我家老姐高中時代的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 老師 怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要以此為交換來做我們的顧問麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想 想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是要從喉嚨中伸出一隻手那般想要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但總覺得要是拿了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的某樣重要的東西就要崩壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是 做得很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這是在做什麼啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦！！ 那你是要來做我們的顧問了唄！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太差勁了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是身為教師不該有的行為…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身為教師之前更是一匹餓狼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魚與熊掌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可兼得！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了櫻井！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然要做 就要朝著全國努力哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs33\pos(718,654)}山頂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始啟動圍棋足球啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從明天開始就要嚴格訓練了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:33.39,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95\pos(150,580)}雪\N飄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:33.39,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fs24\pos(221,580)}flsnow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒～？是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一個叫中之條的傢伙麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中之條君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中之條君 有人找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 有什麼事麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魅力沒了——
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HD6A6FE&\pos(622,498)}與愛有關的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 幫我去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\bord0\shad0\c&H343432&\move(1257,479,934,438,30,364)}油\N漆\N未\N乾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臨時停車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:25.84,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,0)\bord4\blur10\fs75\pos(100,360)}誰\N來\N幫\N幫\N我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水上同學 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.67,0:18:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 竟然帶來這麼多點心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想讓狗咬博士的人！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對就是這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 我去準備點茶水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大威德明王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很帥的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不帥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個 很有意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,36LDK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不算浴室 廁所和窗戶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在畫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藍鯊魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好帥！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 畫一條不一樣的鯊魚看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫一條笑著的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟博士的交換好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\frz16.196\pos(746,395)\c&H2D3232&}回\N去\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士 水上同學回去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是我和她說了下次再來畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來幹什麼了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:32.51,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}知らなかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:32.51,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}從前我並不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:37.33,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}空がこんなに青いとは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:37.33,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}天空竟然能有如此之藍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:41.70,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}手をつないで　歩いて行って
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:41.70,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我們手牽著手 向前緩緩行走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:45.65,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}みんなであおいだ空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:45.65,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}大家一起仰望的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:49.53,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}ほんとに青い空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:49.53,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}天空真的是好藍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:54.68,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}空は教えてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:54.68,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}天空教給了我這些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:59.55,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}大きい心を持つように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:59.55,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}要常懷一顆寬容的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:07.27,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}友だちの手をはなさぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:07.27,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}願牽著朋友們的手再也不放開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:13.67,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}知らなかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:13.67,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}從前我並不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:18.50,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}空がこんなに青いとは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:18.50,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}天空竟然能有如此之藍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:22.83,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}なぜかしら　悲しくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:22.83,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}不知為什麼 變得如此悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.83,0:22:26.47,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}ひとりで見上げた空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.83,0:22:26.47,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}那我一人仰望的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:30.83,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}とっても　青い空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:30.83,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}非常藍的 那天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.96,0:22:35.76,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}空は聞かせてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.96,0:22:35.76,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}天空側過耳來細細聽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.13,0:22:40.64,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}風にも負けない雲のうた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.13,0:22:40.64,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}不會敗給風兒的雲兒的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.14,0:22:48.58,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}ひとりでも　もうなかないように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.14,0:22:48.58,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}就算一個人 也已經不會再哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.02,0:22:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,900)\pos(652,493)\c&H0A0A0A&\shad0\bord0\K100}隻{\K100}言{\K100}片{\K100}語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.26,0:23:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.66,0:23:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是畢業照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.45,0:23:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著照片 連著喊好幾聲「嗚哇 好可愛」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會想著「是說現在不可愛嗎」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一話的日常是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二十四話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待
